%20that.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOur%20columnist%20says%20the%20two%20aren't%20on%20the%20same%20page%20about%20their%20goals%20and%20suggests%20couples%20counseling.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EGot%20a%20question%20for%20our%20columnist%3F%20Write%20to%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%20using%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdhFnAxR57cNtGiwNUd-6vLAYAc75grvly3C10-854vFP4arw%2Fviewform%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2220%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSdhFnAxR57cNtGiwNUd-6vLAYAc75grvly3C10-854vFP4arw%2Fviewform%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22summary_bullets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20Google%20form%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDear%20For%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI've%20always%20been%20a%20career-driven%20person%2C%20partially%20because%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20do%20work%20I'm%20not%20passionate%20about%2C%20but%20also%20because%20I've%20always%20been%20afraid%20of%20not%20being%20able%20to%20provide%20for%20myself%20and%20buy%20the%20things%20I%20want%20and%20need%20to%20be%20happy%20and%20healthy.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI've%20worked%20my%20way%20up%20to%20a%20well-paying%20director%20role%20with%20a%20salary%20that%20provides%20financial%20security%20for%20my%20family.%20The%20only%20problem%20is%20that%20I'm%20burned%20out%20and%20unhappy%2C%20and%20I'm%20starting%20to%20resent%20my%20husband.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20husband%20didn't%20get%20a%20degree%2C%20has%20no%20true%20calling%2C%20and%20is%20content%20to%20get%20a%20meager%20paycheck%20and%20go%20home.%20I%20make%20more%20than%20double%20what%20he%20makes%2C%20so%20I%20carry%20much%20more%20of%20our%20financial%20burden.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20don't%20care%20that%20he's%20not%20as%20driven%20as%20I%20am%2C%20but%20I'm%20exhausted%20and%20stressed%20all%20the%20time.%20I'd%20like%20to%20take%20a%20lower-level%20role%20and%20find%20some%20balance%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20see%20a%20way%20to%20do%20it%20without%20my%20husband%20earning%20more.%20I've%20mentioned%20this%20a%20few%20times%2C%20and%20he%20just%20brushes%20it%20off.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20are%20no%20clear%20career%20growth%20options%20for%20him.%20He%20is%20very%20supportive%20at%20home%2C%20doing%20more%20housework%20and%20caring%20for%20our%20son.%20But%20I'm%20tired%20of%20feeling%20like%20I%20don't%20have%20enough%20energy%20for%20myself%20and%20my%20kid%20because%20work%20is%20so%20draining.%20Can%20you%20see%20another%20way%20for%20us%20to%20work%20this%20out%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESincerely%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERunning%20Out%20of%20Steam%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDear%20Running%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20sound%20tired.%20And%20the%20thing%20about%20marriage%20is%2C%20that's%20the%20point%2C%20right%3F%20A%20lifelong%20arm%20to%20wrap%20around%20our%20waists%20and%20hold%20us%20upright%20as%20we%20limp%20across%20the%20finish%20line.%20Except%2C%20while%20that%20may%20be%20the%20deal%20we%20think%20we're%20getting%2C%20bringing%20two%20people%2C%20two%20histories%2C%20and%20two%20value%20systems%20together%20rarely%20works%20out%20so%20seamlessly%20symbiotically%20%E2%80%94%20at%20least%20not%20without%20effort%20and%20intention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20entered%20our%20relationship%20with%20the%20assumption%20that%20we%20were%20on%20the%20same%20page%20about%20everything.%20This%20isn't%20because%20we%20didn't%20talk%20over%20the%20big%20questions%20or%20have%20premarital%20counseling%3B%20we%20did%20both.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20any%20married%20person%20can%20tell%20you%20%E2%80%94%20you%20might%20think%20you%20agree%20on%20the%20big%20questions%2C%20but%20what%20about%20the%20small%20ones%3F%20Or%20the%20fact%20that%20before%20you're%20in%20it%2C%20those%20big%20questions%20are%20purely%20theoretical.%20What%20about%20when%20you%20change%20your%20mind%20five%20minutes%20into%20the%20theoretical%20becoming%20reality%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20thought%20we%20were%20on%20the%20same%20page%20about%20everything%2C%20and%20when%20that%20assumption%20began%20falling%20apart%2C%20we%20just%20kept%20going%20as%20if%20we%20didn't%20notice.%20Because%20choices%20had%20been%20made%2C%20major%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ffinancial-planning%5C%22%3Efinancial%20plans%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20already%20in%20motion%2C%20and%20no%20one%20likes%20to%20admit%20they're%20going%20back%20on%20their%20word.%20So%2C%20instead%20of%20acknowledging%20that%20we%20didn't%20want%20all%20the%20same%20things%2C%20we%20fought%20around%20the%20issue%20by%20arguing%20over%20our%20different%20energy%20levels%2C%20attitudes%2C%20and%20approaches%20to%20the%20dreams%20we%20still%20supposedly%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExcept%2C%20we%20didn't%20share%20those%20dreams%20anymore.%20And%20as%20bad%20as%20that%20sounds%2C%20not%20wanting%20all%20the%20same%20things%20isn't%20a%20dealbreaker%20for%20us.%20We're%20two%20different%20people.%20Of%20course%2C%20we%20want%20two%20different%20things.%20Because%20while%20we%20may%20be%20on%20several%20different%20pages%20on%20several%20important%20issues%2C%20the%20name%20of%20our%20book%20remains%20the%20same%3A%20Us.%20Our%20marriage%2C%20our%20family%2C%20our%20love.%20We%20want%20those%20things%20more%20than%20anything%20else%20in%20the%20world%2C%20so%20we%20will%20fight%20for%20them%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20see%20this%20in%20your%20letter%20%E2%80%94%20an%20assumption%20that%20you%20share%20the%20same%20goals%3A%20financial%20security%2C%20a%20certain%20standard%20of%20living%2C%20and%20a%20specific%20method%20for%20achieving%20both.%20But%20it%20seems%20this%20assumption%20has%20begun%20to%20fall%20apart.%20You're%20driven%20and%20career-oriented%2C%20and%20you%20equate%20compensation%2C%20high%20energy%2C%20and%20ambition%20with%20happiness%20and%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20your%20husband%20seems%20to%20equate%20peace%20and%20ease%20with%20happiness%20and%20success.%20As%20you're%20currently%20experiencing%2C%20these%20ideas%20aren't%20compatible.%20Fortunately%2C%20they%20don't%20need%20to%20be.%20You%20and%20your%20husband%20don't%20have%20to%20agree%20on%20what%20the%20good%20life%20looks%20like%2C%20but%20you%20do%20have%20to%20honor%20the%20other's%20perspective%2C%20and%20to%20do%20that%2C%20you%20have%20to%20know%20what%20the%20other's%20perspective%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20lines%20in%20your%20letter%20stood%20out%20to%20me.%20The%20first%20is%20when%20you%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe's%20not%20as%20driven%20as%20I%20am.%26quot%3B%20The%20second%20is%20when%20you%20tell%20your%20husband%20about%20your%20burnout%2C%20he%20%26quot%3Bbrushes%20it%20off.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20opinion%20that%20he%20isn't%20driven%20stood%20out%20to%20me%20because%20it%20tells%20me%20you%20blame%20his%20unwillingness%20to%20do%20more%20financially%20on%20his%20personality.%20This%20is%20an%20assumption%20you're%20making.%20Not%20striving%20to%20become%20the%20CEO%20of%20a%20Fortune%20500%20company%20doesn't%20mean%20your%20husband%20simply%20isn't%20interested%20in%20helping%20you%20pay%20your%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-mortgage-lenders%5C%22%3Emortgage%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20brings%20me%20to%20the%20second%20thing%20you%20mentioned%20in%20your%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20try%20to%20talk%20to%20him%20about%20your%20stress%20and%20frustration%2C%20he%20brushes%20you%20off.%20Here%20you%20are%2C%20telling%20him%20you're%20scared%20and%20exhausted%2C%20asking%20him%20to%20be%20there%20for%20you%2C%20and%20he's%20not%20even%20engaging%20with%20you%20in%20your%20crisis.%20That%20sounds%20like%20something%20much%20deeper%20than%20a%20lack%20of%20drive.%20It%20sounds%20like%20he%20is%20on%20a%20completely%20different%20page%20than%20you%2C%20and%20he's%20too%20scared%20to%20tell%20you%20what%20it%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdmitting%20that%20he's%20changed%20his%20mind%20or%20didn't%20even%20know%20himself%20well%20enough%20back%20when%20you%20first%20fell%20in%20love%20to%20make%20sweeping%20declarations%20about%20his%20dreams%20is%20probably%20very%20hard%20for%20him.%20So%20hard%2C%20he%20may%20not%20be%20able%20to%20tell%20you%20at%20all%2C%20especially%20in%20time%20to%20save%20you%20from%20clinical%20burnout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20suggest%20you%20try%20couples%20counseling.%20Therapy%20will%20offer%20him%20a%20safe%20space%20to%20speak%20his%20truth%20and%20provide%20you%20both%20with%20an%20expert%20to%20help%20guide%20you%20back%20to%20one%20another%20until%20you're%20close%20enough%20for%20your%20husband%20to%20wrap%20his%20arm%20around%20your%20waist%20and%20hold%20you%20up%20across%20the%20finish%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERooting%20for%20you%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Love%20%26amp%3B%20Money%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinding%20a%20financial%20advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20hard.%20SmartAsset's%20free%20tool%20matches%20you%20with%20up%20to%20three%20fiduciary%20financial%20advisors%20that%20serve%20your%20area%20in%20minutes.%20Each%20advisor%20has%20been%20vetted%20by%20SmartAsset%20and%20is%20held%20to%20a%20fiduciary%20standard%20to%20act%20in%20your%20best%20interests.%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__f