nese%20officials%20or%20the%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20he%20spent%20to%20buy%20access%20to%20or%20time%20with%20celebrities%20or%20politicians%20or%20investments%20for%20which%20he%20grossly%20overpaid%20having%20done%20zero%20diligence%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BThe%20harm%20was%20vast.%20The%20remorse%20is%20nonexistent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recovered%20calculations%2C%20too%2C%20distort%20how%20much%20money%20customers%20are%20actually%20getting%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFTX's%20depositors%20would%20be%20repaid%20based%20on%20the%20dollar%20value%20of%20their%20cryptocurrency%20holdings%20at%20the%20time%20that%20FTX%20declared%20bankruptcy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20if%20someone%20purchased%20one%20bitcoin%20on%20FTX's%20exchange%20at%20the%20price%20of%20%2460%2C000%2C%20and%20then%20bitcoin%20dropped%20to%20%2420%2C000%20in%20November%20of%202022%20%E2%80%94%20which%20can%20be%20at%20least%20partly%20attributed%20to%20the%20chaos%20of%20FTX%20at%20the%20time%20%E2%80%94%20their%20credit%20is%20worth%20%2420%2C000.%20It%20doesn't%20matter%20if%20the%20price%20of%20bitcoin%20has%20risen%20back%20to%20over%20%2460%2C000%20since%20then.%20The%20creditor%20would%20get%20%2420%2C000%2C%20not%20%2460%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20value%20of%20FTX's%20assets%20after%20bankruptcy%20ultimately%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20Bankman-Fried%2C%20pointed%20out%20Rachel%20Maimin%2C%20a%20former%20New%20York%20federal%20prosecutor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20circumstances%20of%20the%20offense%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20Maimin%2C%20now%20a%20white-collar%20defense%20attorney%20at%20Lowenstein%20Sandler%20LLP%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20totally%20separate%20from%20that.%20This%20is%20something%20that%20happened%20almost%20by%20luck%20after%20the%20offense%20was%20complete.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESBF's%20lawyers%20and%20family%20suggest%20he's%20neurodivergent%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried's%20lawyers%20and%20family%20members%20have%20made%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.courtlistener.com%2Frecap%2Fgov.uscourts.nysd.590940%2Fgov.uscourts.nysd.590940.407.0_3.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eother%20entreaties%20to%20the%20judge%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20have%20said%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-parents-sentencing-submission-danger-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexhibits%20behavioral%20characteristics%20associated%20with%20neurodivergent%20people%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20asked%20Kaplan%20to%20judge%20him%20accordingly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20genuinely%20fear%20for%20Sam's%20life%20in%20the%20typical%20prison%20environment%2C%26quot%3B%20Barbara%20Fried%2C%20his%20mother%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20judge.%20%26quot%3BSam's%20outward%20presentation%2C%20his%20inability%20to%20read%20or%20respond%20appropriately%20to%20many%20social%20cues%2C%20and%20his%20touching%20but%20naive%20belief%20in%20the%20power%20of%20facts%20and%20reason%20to%20resolve%20disputes%2C%20put%20him%20in%20extreme%20danger.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeurodiversity%20can%20express%20itself%20in%20an%20enormous%20range%20of%20ways%2C%20including%20autism%2C%20dyslexia%2C%20or%20attention-deficit%2Fhyperactivity%20disorder.%20His%20defense%20attorneys%20and%20family%20have%20left%20his%20experience%20undefined%20and%20have%20not%20given%20any%20indication%20that%20he%20has%20undergone%20any%20diagnostic%20tests.%20Prosecutors%2C%20in%20their%20116-page%20sentencing%20memorandum%2C%20did%20not%20address%20the%20topic%20of%20Bankman-Fried's%20alleged%20neurodiversity%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20say%20Bankman-Fried's%20life%20and%20characteristics%20%E2%80%94%20he%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20stable%20home%20with%20caring%20parents%2C%20went%20to%20an%20elite%20college%2C%20and%20worked%20at%20an%20elite%20Wall%20Street%20trading%20firm%20%E2%80%94%20show%20that%20he%