ewives%20goes%20back%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIs%20Bravo%20doomed%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20network%2C%20long%20beloved%20by%20reality%20TV%20fans%20for%20gifting%20us%20drama-filled%20franchises%20like%20%26quot%3BThe%20Real%20Housewives%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BVanderpump%20Rules%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BBelow%20Deck%2C%26quot%3B%20is%20facing%20legal%20action%20from%20a%20number%20of%20former%20stars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20underlying%20argument%20in%20all%20three%20claims%20is%20the%20same%3A%20They%20believe%20the%20network%2C%20associated%20production%20companies%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20longtime%20host%20Andy%20Cohen%20are%20purposely%20fostering%20a%20negative%20working%20environment%2C%20rampant%20with%20favoritism%20and%20filled%20with%20toxicity%20geared%20toward%20maximizing%20the%20drama%20%E2%80%94%20often%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20stars'%20safety%20and%20well-being.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20complete%20rundown%20of%20the%20lawsuits%20filed%20and%20threatened%20against%20Cohen%20and%20the%20network%2C%20and%20a%20look%20at%20the%20deep-rooted%20issues%20other%20stars%20say%20have%20been%20simmering%20there%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(Representatives%20for%20Bravo%2C%20NBCUniversal%2C%20and%20Peacock%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%20Shed%20Media%20could%20not%20be%20reached%20for%20comment%20by%20email%20or%20phone.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECaroline%20Manzo%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20Bravo%20in%20January%202024%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202024%2C%20Caroline%20Manzo%2C%20formerly%20an%20original%20cast%20member%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Real%20Housewives%20of%20New%20Jersey%2C%26quot%3B%20filed%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20Bravo%20and%20other%20related%20entities%2C%20including%20NBCUniversal%20(which%20owns%20Bravo)%2C%20Peacock%20(the%20streaming%20service%20that%20distributes%20the%20network's%20shows)%2C%20and%20Shed%20Media%20(a%20production%20company%20behind%20several%20Bravo%20series).%3C%2Fp%