usewives-ultimate-girls-trip-morocco-may-never-air%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshelved%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Freal-housewives-rhony-legacy-ulimate-girls-trip-premiere-date-ex-wives-club-1235686185%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eits%20premiere%20date%20swapped%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20different%20season%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Real%20Housewives%20Ultimate%20Girls%20Trip%3A%20RHONY%20Legacy%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20aired%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20filing%2C%20Manzo%20says%20she's%20seeking%20damages%20after%20Bravo%20discriminated%20and%20retaliated%20against%20her%20for%20speaking%20out%20about%20Glanville's%20harassment.%20She%20also%20accuses%20the%20network%20of%20plying%20Glanville%20%26quot%3Bwith%20copious%20amounts%20of%20alcohol%20so%20that%20she%20would%20act%20outrageous%20and%20sexually%20harass%20others%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bencourage%20and%20direct%26quot%3B%20Glanville%20to%20harass%20Manzo%20and%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20also%20points%20to%20several%20instances%20of%20Glanville's%20%26quot%3Bsexually%20harassing%20and%20assaulting%20behavior%26quot%3B%20on%20other%20Bravo%20shows%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20network%20was%20aware%20of%20her%20tendencies%20and%20continued%20to%20cast%20her%20regardless%2C%20undermining%20the%20safety%20of%20other%20cast%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlanville%20herself%20isn't%20named%20as%20a%20defendant%20in%20Manzo's%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EManzo's%20lawyer%2C%20Derek%20Smith%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20via%20email%20that%20Manzo%20didn't%20have%20additional%20comment%2C%20but%20shared%20the%20following%20statement%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20production%20company's%20creative%20rights%20should%20never%20trump%20a%20cast%20member's%20safety.%20I%20get%20it%3A%20Shocking%20reality%20television%20brings%20the%20ratings%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20reads%2C%20in%20part.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20human%20decency%20requires%20that%20we%20put%20limits%20on%20that%20shocking%20behavior.%20We%20all%20have%20the%20right%20to%20work%20in%20an%20environment%20that%20is%20free%20of%20sexual%20harassment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20continues%3A%20%26quot%3BPeople%20like%20Ms.%C2%A0Manzo%C2%A0should%20never%20be%20sexually%20harassed%20in%20order%20to%20get%20a%20'good'%20shot.%20These%20are%20people.%20They%20are%20not%20pawns%20for%20production%20companies%20to%20abuse%20for%20ratings%20and%20profits.%20Fortunately%2C%20there%20are%20laws%20in%20effect%20to%20protect%20reality%20TV%20cast%20members.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBrandi%20Glanville%20threatened%20a%20lawsuit%20against%20Andy%20Cohen%20in%20February%202024%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGlanville's%20attorneys%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20NBCUniversal%2C%20Warner%20Bros.%2C%20and%20Shed%20Media%2C%20which%20produced%20%26quot%3BUltimate%20Girls%20Trip%2C%26quot%3B%20threatening%20a%20lawsuit%20and%20accusing%20Andy%20Cohen%20of%20sexual%20harassment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20eight-page%20letter%2C%20viewed%20by%20BI%2C%20Glanville's%20lawyers%20claim%20that%20an%20%26quot%3Bobviously%20inebriated%26quot%3B%20Cohen%20sent%20Glanville%20a%20video%20in%202022%20talking%20about%20%26quot%3Bhis%20intention%20to%20sleep%20with%20another%20Bravo%20star%20that%20night%20while%20thinking%20of%20her%20and%20invited%20her%20to%20watch%20via%20FaceTime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Cohen%20was%20Ms.%20Glanville's%20boss%20at%20the%20time%20and%20exercised%20complete%20and%20total%20control%20over%20her%20career.%20This%20was%20an%20extraordinary%20abuse%20of%20power%20that%20left%20Ms.%20Glanville%20feeling%20trapped%20and%20disgusted%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20reads.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20inconceivable%20that%20Mr.%20Cohen%20remains%20in%20his%20post%20in%20spite%20of%C2%A0this%20behavior%20and%20harkens%20back%20to%20the%20bad%20old%20days%20of%20Matt%20Lauer%20and%20NBC%20News%20when%20profits%20were%20prioritized