e%20by%20elite%20units%20such%20as%20the%203rd%20Assault%20Brigade%2C%20superior%20Russian%20firepower%20and%20a%20critical%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-losing-ammunition-battle-forces-being-outshot-by-russia-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elack%20of%20artillery%20ammunition%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20eventually%20left%20Ukrainian%20commanders%20with%20a%20grim%20choice%3A%20hold%20Avdiivka%20and%20risk%20encirclement%20and%20destruction%2C%20or%20retreat%20and%20hand%20Russia%20a%20symbolic%20victory.%20Wisely%20realizing%20that%20it%20was%20better%20to%20save%20an%20army%20to%20fight%20another%20day%2C%20the%20Ukrainians%20had%20to%20conduct%20one%20of%20the%20most%20difficult%20military%20operations%3A%20a%20retreat%20under%20heavy%20enemy%20fire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20Ukraine%20managed%20to%20extract%20the%20bulk%20of%20its%20forces%2C%20the%20operation%20did%20not%20go%20smoothly.%20%26quot%3BWithdrawal%20from%20the%20completely%20encircled%20'Zenit'%20position%20in%20the%20southeastern%20outskirts%20of%20Avdiivka%20was%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fen-us%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fukrainian-soldiers-recall-retreat-from-avdiivka-on-foot-leaving-their-wounded-behind%2Far-BB1iCbcF%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eparticularly%20difficult%20affair%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20Ukrainian%20forces%2C%20with%20witness%20reporting%20of%20a%20disorganized%20nighttime%20movement%20under%20attack%20from%20Russian%20artillery%2C%20direct%20fire%2C%20unmanned%20aerial%20vehicles%2C%20and%20loitering%20munitions%2C%26quot%3B%20Forte%20noted.%20Hundreds%20of%20soldiers%20were%20reportedly%20captured%2C%20and%20some%20were%20executed%20while%20trying%20to%20surrender.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20soldiers%20at%20Kasserine%20Pass%20in%20Tunisia%5C%22%20charset