%20types%20of%20retreats%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Delay%20operations%20mean%20sacrificing%20ground%20while%20slowing%20the%20enemy%20advance%2C%20while%20retirement%20involves%20forces%20not%20engaged%20in%20combat%20moving%20further%20away%20from%20the%20enemy.%20It%20is%20withdrawal%20operations%20%E2%80%94%20which%20mean%20disengaging%20from%20combat%2C%20as%20the%20Ukrainians%20had%20to%20perform%20at%20Avdiivka%20%E2%80%94%20that%20are%20particularly%20difficult.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EForte%20points%20to%20two%20lessons%20that%20the%20US%20Army%20should%20learn%20from%20the%20battle.%20First%2C%20withdrawals%20must%20be%20carefully%20planned.%20The%20Ukrainian%20retreat%20suffered%20from%20poor%20coordination%20between%20the%20110th%20Mechanized%20Brigade%20that%20had%20been%20defending%20the%20city%2C%20and%20the%20newly%20arrived%203rd%20Assault%20Brigade%20that%20was%20supposed%20to%20cover%20the%20110th's%20withdrawal.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BPrimary%20and%20alternate%20routes%20need%20to%20be%20established%2C%20as%20does%20the%20timing%20of%20their%20use%2C%20recognition%20signals%2C%20and%20methods%20of%20communication%2C%26quot%3B%20Forte%20warned.%20%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20if%20an%20element%20of%20the%20withdrawing%20force's%20main%20body%20begins%20its%20movement%20before%20the%20security%20force%20is%20in%20position%20to%20effectively%20support%2C%20it%20may%20be%20preemptively%20engaged%20and%20destroyed%20during%20this%20period%20of%20vulnerability.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBattlefield%20movement%20%E2%80%94%20including%20retreats%20%E2%80%94%20has%20become%20difficult%20in%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20because%20of%20the%20constant%20presence%20of%20surveillance%20and%20explosive%20drones.%20But%20the%20biggest%20problem%20may%20be%20evacuating%20casualties%3B%20at%20Avdiivka%2C%20some%20wounded%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20were%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2024%2F02%2F19%2Feurope%2Fukrainian-avdiivka-soldiers-messages-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eleft%20behind%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%26quot%3BMedical%20evacuation%20procedures%20must%20be%20addressed%20in%20detail%2C%20to%20include%20designated%20vehicles%2C%20routes%2C%20and%20link-up%20points%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Forte.%20%26quot%3BBased%20on%20available%20time%20and%20enemy%20action%2C%20the%20ability%20to%20evacuate%20all%20casualties%20may%20not%20be%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20other%20lesson%20of%20Avdiivka%20is%20ensuring%20adequate%20support%20for%20a%20retreat%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20covering%20force%20that%20screens%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20army.%20%26quot%3BTo%20accomplish%20this%20task%2C%20in%20which%20the%20security%20force%20is%20potentially%20outnumbered%20or%20outgunned%2C%20it%20will%20need%20prioritization%20from%20higher%20echelons%20for%20key%20enablers%20and%20weapons%20systems%2C%20such%20as%20air%20defense%2C%20fuel%20depots%2C%20and%20counterbattery%20radar%2C%26quot%3B%20Forte%20said.%20Or%2C%20mine%20clearance%20equipment%20must%20be%20available%20in%20case%20the%20enemy%20uses%20artillery%20to%20drop%20instant%20minefields%20along%20withdrawal%20routes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20their%20credit%2C%20and%20despite%20a%20lack%20of%20ammunition%2C%20Ukrainian%20commanders%20were%20able%20to%20provide%20some%20fire%20support%20for%20the%20retreat.%20%26quot%3BUkrainian%20military%20leaders%20were%20able%20to%20adjust%20prioritization%20of%20key%20weapon%20systems%20to%20maintain%20indirect%20fire%20effects%20that%20effectively%20enabled%20friendly%20movement%20and%20maneuver%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Forte.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20while%20Avdiivka%20wasn't%20a%20Ukrainian%20victory%2C%20the%20battle%20could%20have%20ended%20a%20lot%20worse.%20%26quot%3BThe%20loss%20of%20Avdiivka%20after%20its%20resolute%20defense%20for%20so%20long%20is%20surely%20a%20bitter%20pill%20to%20swallow%2C%20but%20the%20Ukrainian%20withdrawal's%20successful%20execution%20preserves%20experienced%20manpower%20and%20meaningful%20military%20capacity%20that%20can%20be%20brought%20to%20bear%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Forte%20concluded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BA%20withdrawal%20does%20not%20intrinsically%20mean%20a%20defeat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BBut%20failing%20to%20train%2C%20plan%2C%20and%20resource%20a%20withdrawal%20could%20result%20in%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Forbes%2C%20Defense%20News%2C%20Foreign%20Policy%20magazine%2C%20and%20other%20publications.%20He%20holds%20an%20MA%20in%20political%20science%20from%20Rutgers%20Univ.%20Follow%20him%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2F%40mipeck1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ETwitter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmipeck%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-the-us-army-should-learn-from-ukraines-hasty-retreat-in-the-battle-of-avdiivka-2024-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711274461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65fdbea62417f97b87ce7ad0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-the-us-army-should-learn-from-ukraines-hasty-retreat-in-the-battle-of-avdiivka-2024-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukraine's%20withdrawal%20under%20heavy%20fire%20in%