E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20had%20pleaded%20not%20guilty%20and%20his%20attorneys%20have%20said%20that%20they%20intend%20to%20appeal%20his%20conviction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttorneys%20Stephen%20Houze%20and%20Jacob%20Houze%2C%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20CNN%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20appeal%2C%20and%20we%20are%20confident%20that%20his%20convictions%20will%20be%20overturned.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20how%20chewing%20gum%20linked%20Mr%20Robert%20to%20the%20case%2C%20the%20statement%20by%20the%20district%20attorney%20revealed%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%202000%2C%20vaginal%20swabs%20taken%20during%20Ms%20Tucker's%20autopsy%20were%20sent%20to%20the%20Oregon%20State%20Police%20(OSP)%20Crime%20Lab%20for%20analysis.%20The%20Crime%20Lab%20developed%20a%20DNA%20profile%20from%20the%20swabs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20when%20the%20detectives%20conducting%20surveillance%20saw%20Mr%20Robert%20spitting%20a%20chewing%20gum%2C%20they%20collected%20it%20and%20submitted%20it%20to%20the%20OSP%20Crime%20Lab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%202021%2C%20a%20genealogist%20with%20Parabon%20Nanolabs%20identified%20Robert%20Plympton%20as%20a%20likely%20contributor%20to%20the%20unknown%20DNA%20profile%20developed%20in%202000.%20Detectives%20with%20the%20Gresham%20Police%20Department%20found%20Plympton%20living%20in%20Troutdale%20and%20began%20conducting%20surveillance.%20When%20they%20saw%20Plympton%20spit%20a%20piece%20of%20chewing%20gum%20onto%20the%20ground%2C%20detectives%20collected%20the%20gum%20and%20submitted%20it%20to%20the%20OSP%20Crime%20Lab.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20continued%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20lab%20determined%20the%20DNA%20profile%20developed%20from%20the%20chewing%20gum%20matched%20the%20DNA%20profile%20developed%20from%20Ms.%20Tucker's%20vaginal%20swabs.%20On%20June%208%2C%202021%2C%20Plympton%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20and%20lodged%20at%20the%20Multnomah%20County%20Detention%20Center.%E2%8