375.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Demanding%20Answers%2C%20Father%20Of%20Budaun%20Murder%20Victims%20Sets%20Bike%20On%20Fire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20father%20of%20the%20two%20children%20brutally%20murdered%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Budaun%2C%20concerned%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20clarity%20surrounding%20the%20motive%20behind%20the%20double%20murder%2C%20set%20a%20bike%20on%20fire%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fire%20brigade%20team%20successfully%20brought%20the%20fire%20under%20control.%20Senior%20Budaun%20police%20officer%20Alok%20Mishra%20arrived%20at%20the%20scene%2C%20and%20the%20in-charge%20of%20the%20Civil%20Line%20police%20station%2C%20Gaurav%20Vishnoi%2C%20held%20discussions%20with%20the%20family%20members%2C%20trying%20to%20make%20them%20understand%20that%20motive%20for%20the%20murders%20will%20only%20be%20disclosed%20following%20the%20investigation%20of%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20police%2C%20Sajid%2C%20a%20familiar%20face%20in%20the%20neighborhood%20who%20ran%20a%20barber%20shop%20opposite%20the%20victims'%20residence%2C%20was%20responsible%20for%20the%20double%20murder.%20Sajid%2C%20known%20to%20the%20children's%20father%2C%20Vinod%20Singh%2C%20visited%20their%20house%20under%20the%20guise%20of%20borrowing%20Rs%205%2C000.%20However%2C%20moments%20after%20being%20handed%20the%20money%2C%20Sajid%20launched%20a%20savage%20assault%20on%20the%20children%20as%20their%20mother%20prepared%20tea%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20gaining%20entry%20into%20the%20household%2C%20Sajid%20allegedly%20asked%20Aayush%20(11)%20to%20take%20him%20to%20his%20mother's%20beauty%20salon%20upstairs.%20Upon%20reaching%20the%20second%20floor%2C%20Sajid%20allegedly%20switched%20off%20the%20lights%20before%20launching%20a%20vicious%20assault%20on%20Aayush%20with%20a%20knife.%20As%20Sajid%20slashed%20Aayush's%20throat%2C%20his%20younger%20brother%20Ahaan%20(6)%20entered%20th