mily%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigation%20into%20the%20case%20is%20still%20ongoing%20with%20the%20police%20trying%20to%20establish%20the%20motive%20behind%20the%20gruesome%20murders.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711268340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Ft6523es8_budaun-double-murder-_625x300_24_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdemanding-answers-father-of-budaun-murder-victims-sets-bike-on-fire-5301454%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20father%20of%20the%20two%20children%20brutally%20murdered%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Budaun%2C%20concerned%20over%20the%20lack%20of%20clarity%20surrounding%20the%20motive%20behind%20the%20double%20murder%2C%20set%20a%20bike%20on%20fire%20on%20Sunday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdemanding-answers-father-of-budaun-murder-victims-sets-bike-on-fire-5301454%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SSEL%20aims%20to%20make%20new%20plant%20operational%20in%20Jul-Sep%20qtr%2C%20says%20CMD%20Reddy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711268138000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-04%2F19%2Ffull%2F1681901132-3901.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fssel-aims-to-make-new-plant-operational-in-jul-sep-qtr-says-cmd-reddy-124032400196_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Reddy%20further%20said%20SSEL%20is%20also%20into%20transmission%20EPC%20projects%20and%20around%2050%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20conductors'%20production%20will%20be%20consumed%20by%20the%20company's%20transmission%20business%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fssel-aims-to-make-new-plant-operational-in-jul-sep-qtr-sa