little%20bit%20easy%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20told%20Star%20Sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Russell%20was%20undoubtedly%20brilliant%20with%20the%20bat%2C%20Gavaskar%20also%20highlighted%20how%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20bowlers%20failed%20to%20execute%20their%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20saw%20someone%20like%20Bhuveneshwar%20Kumar%2C%20who%20was%20practising%20his%20yorkers%20so%20well%20on%20the%20practise%20pitches%2C%20bowled%20leg-deliveries%20(in%20the%20match)%20which%20was%20everything%20in%20the%20arc%20for%20Andre%20Russell...%20When%20somebody%20like%20Russell%20is%20hitting%20the%20ball%20into%20the%20stands%2C%20nobody%20can%20stop%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20game%2C%20Russell%20gave%20a%20little%20emotional%20speech%2C%20highlighting%20his%20love%20for%20the%20Knight%20Riders%20and%20what%20wearing%20the%20franchise's%20jersey%20means%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20stuff%20pop%20on%20my%20Insta%20and%20I%20realise%20how%20well%20I%20am%20striking%20the%20ball.%20Shows%20that%20you%20are%20doing%20well.%20I%20have%20tried%20to%20react%20with%20whatever%20comes%20my%20way.%20Over%20the%20last%202%20years%2C%20bowlers%20have%20their%20plans%20against%20me.%20I%20have%20been%20digging%20out%20the%20runs%2C%20and%20I%20know%20everyone%20has%20a%20plan%20for%20me.%20(On%20his%20journey%20with%20KKR)%20I%20was%20on%20the%20bench%20early%20on%2C%20and%20just%20tried%20to%20make%20myself%20useful.%20This%20franchise%20means%20a%20lot%20to%20me%2C%20what%20I%20did%20tonight%20was%20just%20a%20way%20to%20prove%20what%20this%20jersey%20means%20to%20me.%20Hopefully%20I%20can%20keep%20performing%20this%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711263300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fddabl5go_gambhir-and-russell-bcci_625x300_24_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fnothing-