0Thursday%20and%2C%20the%20next%20day%2C%20the%20Rouse%20Avenue%20court%20in%20the%20city%20had%20remanded%20him%20in%20the%20Probe%20Agency's%20custody%20till%20March%2028.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Order%20From%20Jail%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtishi%2C%20while%20addressing%20a%20press%20conference%20this%20morning%2C%20said%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20has%20directed%20the%20department%20to%20ensure%20adequate%20water%20supply%20in%20the%20affected%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20suggested%20the%20minister%20to%20seek%20the%20help%20of%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20VK%20Saxena%2C%20if%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'I%20have%20learnt%20that%20people%20are%20facing%20water%20and%20sewer%20related%20issues%20in%20parts%20of%20Delhi.%20I%20am%20worried%20about%20this.%20People%20shouldn't%20face%20these%20problems%20because%20I%20am%20in%20jail.%20Tankers%20should%20be%20arranged%20for%20places%20where%20there%20is%20a%20scarcity%20of%20water%20and%20appropriate%20directions%20should%20be%20issued%20to%20the%20officials%20so%20that%20people%20don't%20face%20any%20problem'%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%20in%20his%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMessage%20From%20Jail%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20yesterday%20urged%20everyone%20to%20continue%20working%20for%20the%20society%20and%20not%20hate%20anyone%2C%20even%20those%20from%20the%20ruling%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20message%20was%20read%20out%20by%20his%20wife%20Sunita%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20several%20forces%20within%20and%20outside%20India%20that%20are%20weakening%20the%20country.%20There%20is%20no%20jail%20that%20can%20keep%20him%20behind%20bars%20for%20long.%20I%20will%20come%20out%20soon%20and%20keep%20my%20promises%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20in%20his%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20The%20Prison%20Rules%20Say%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20law%20officer%20of%20Delhi's%20Tihar%20Jail%20says%20that%20an%20inmate%20can%20only%20hold%20two%20meetings%20in%20a%20week%2C%20which%20would%20make%20it%20difficult%20for%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20to%20carry%20out%20his%20responsibilities%20as%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20measure%20that%20could%20facilitate%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20governance%20from%20within%20the%20confinement%20was%20if%20he%20was%20put%20under%20house%20arrest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20has%20the%20power%20to%20convert%20any%20building%20into%20a%20prison%2C%20and%20if%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20can%20convince%20him%20to%20put%20him%20under%20house%20arrest%20-%20it%20would%20help%20him%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20day-to-day%20functioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20administrator%20has%20the%20authority%20to%20declare%20any%20building%20as%20a%20jail%2C%26quot%3B%20Sunil%20Gupta%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711260120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fqharjlh_arvind-kejriwal-vk-saxena_625x300_08_June_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-arvind-kejriwal-arrested-arvind-kejriwal-jailed-aap-bjp-ed-custody-delhi-chief-minister-atishi-how-arvind-kejriwal-passed-his-1st-orde-5300872%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20last%20evening%20issued%20an%20order%20from%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20lock-up%20for%20the%20areas%20facing%20water%20shortage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-arvind-kejriwal-arrested-arvind-kejriwal-jailed-aap-bjp-ed-custody-delhi-chief-minister-atishi-how-arvind-kejriwal-passed-his-1st-orde-5300872%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Metro%20Responds%20After%20Video%20Of%20Girls%2