ve%20increased%20the%20number%20of%20ghost%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20also%20added%20that%20it%20might%20be%20due%20to%20companies%20being%20unsure%20of%20the%20future%20and%20hiring%20new%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20worth%20noting%20that%20several%20ghost%20job%20listings%20don't%20even%20have%20a%20job%20description%20but%20include%20a%20long%20list%20of%20perks%20to%20convince%20a%20candidate%20to%20apply.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20can%20you%20tell%20if%20the%20job%20is%20real%20or%20not%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGenuine%20job%20postings%20will%20always%20include%20specific%20details%20about%20the%20expectations%20for%20the%20role%2C%20qualifications%20and%20responsibilities.%20Therefore%2C%20if%20a%20candidate%20comes%20across%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fkaradennison%2F2023%2F11%2F27%2Fhow-ghost-job-postings-are-creating-a-false-sense-of-hope%2F%3Fsh%3D398860057dc0%5C%22%3Ea%20vague%20job%20description%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20reads%20like%20a%20generic%20template%2C%20then%20that%20is%20your%20clue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20candidate%20applies%20for%20a%20job%20and%20doesn't%20get%20a%20response%20for%20weeks%20or%20even%20months%20in%20some%20cases%20then%20that%20means%20he%2Fshe%20fell%20for%20a%20ghost%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20a%20candidate%20comes%20across%20the%20same%20job%20opening%20repeatedly%20over%20an%20extended%20period%20could%20also%20serve%20as%20a%20warning%20sign.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711259160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fj67moja8_job-interview-generic_625x300_10_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fall-you-need-to-know-about-ghost-jobs-the-rising-trend-in-hiring-5300521%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ghost%20jobs%20are%20vacancies%20that%20a%20company%20advertises%20about%20but%20has%20no%20intention%20of%20filling.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22