th-india-says-pakistan-foreign-minister%2Famp_articleshow%2F108744325.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22NCERT%20Set%20To%20Release%20New%20Textbooks%2C%20Syllabus%20For%20CBSE%20Classes%203%2C%206%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20recent%20announcement%2C%20the%20Central%20Board%20of%20Secondary%20Education%20(CBSE)%20has%20communicated%20that%20the%20National%20Council%20of%20Educational%20Research%20and%20Training%20(NCERT)%20will%20be%20introducing%20new%20syllabi%20and%20textbooks%20for%20classes%203%20and%206%20for%20the%20academic%20year%202024-25%2C%20starting%20April%201.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20classes%20will%20continue%20with%20the%20existing%20curriculum%20and%20textbooks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBSE%2C%20in%20a%20communique%20sent%20to%20all%20affiliated%20institutions%2C%20stated%20that%20NCERT%2C%20in%20a%20letter%20dated%20March%2018%2C%20has%20revealed%20its%20ongoing%20development%20of%20new%20syllabi%20and%20textbooks%20for%20classes%20third%20and%20sixth.%20Schools%20have%20been%20advised%20to%20transition%20to%20these%20new%20materials%2C%20replacing%20NCERT-published%20textbooks%20until%20the%20year%202023.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThese%20initiatives%20are%20part%20of%20the%20larger%20framework%20outlined%20in%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%202020%2C%20particularly%20focusing%20on%20the%20new%20national%20curriculum%20framework%20for%20school%20education%20(NCF-SE)%202023.%20As%20per%20the%20CBSE%20statement%2C%20a%20bridge%20course%20for%20class%20six%20and%20concise%20guidelines%20for%20class%20three%20are%20in%20the%20works%20to%20facilitate%20a%20smooth%20transition%20aligned%20with%20NCF-SE%202023.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BA%20bridge%20course%20for%20class%206%2C%20and%20concise%20guidelines%20for%20class%203%20are%20being%20developed%20by%20NCERT%20for%20facilitating%20a%20seamless%20transition%20for%20students%20to%20new%20pedagogical%20practices%20and%20areas%20of%20study%20aligned%20with%20NCF-SE%202023.%20These%20resources%20will%20be%20disseminated%20to%20all%20the%20schools%20online%20once%20they%20are%20received%20from%20NCERT%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20board%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20the%20CBSE%20has%20announced%20plans%20to%20conduct%20capacity-building%20programs%20for%20school%20heads%20and%20teachers%2C%20aimed%20at%20familiarising%20them%20with%20the%20new%20teaching-learning%20methodologies%20envisaged%20in%20NEP-2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20no%20change%20in%20the%20Curriculum%20and%20textbooks%20for%20other%20classes%20for%20the%20academic%20year%202024-25%20commencing%20from%20April%201%2C%202024%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CBSE%20said.%20Schools%20have%20been%20urged%20to%20adopt%20the%20recommendations%20outlined%20in%20NCF-SE%202023%2C%20incorporating%20methodologies%20like%20multilingualism%2C%20art-integrated%20education%2C%20and%20experiential%20learning%20where%20feasible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBSE%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BSchools%20are%20advised%20to%20align%20their%20practices%20with%20the%20recommendations%20delineated%20in%20NCF-SE-2023.%20This%20includes%20adherence%20to%20guidelines%20concerning%20content%2C%20pedagogical%20strategies%2C%20assessment%20methodologies%2C%20and%20other%20pertinent%20areas%20as%20communicated%20by%20the%20board%20from%20time%20to%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20development%20follows%20NCERT's%20rationalisation%20of%20syllabi%20for%20classes%206%20to%2012%20in%202022%2C%20aimed%20at%20reducing%20the%20content%20load%20on%20students%20during%20the%20Covid-19%20pandemic.%20Notable%20changes%20included%20the%20removal%20of%20chapters%20on%20various%20historical%20and%20political%20topics.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711258260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-05%2Fu55173rg_cbsekids_650x400_08_May_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fncert-set-to-release-new-textbooks-syllabus-for-cbse-classes-3-6-5300711%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20CBSE%20said%20there%20would%20be%20no%20change%20in%20the%20curriculum%20and%20textbooks%20for%20other%20classes%20for%20the%20academic%20year%202024-25%20starting%20April%201%2C%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fncert-set-to-release-new-textbooks-syllabus-for-cbse-classes-3-6-5300711%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22University%20students%20become%20tram%20operators%20as%20Germany%20faces%20manpower%20shortage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711257846000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108744453%2Cimgsize-534230.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Funiversity-students-become-tram-operators-as-germany-faces-manpower-shortage%2Farticleshow%2F108743993.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108743993.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Funiversity-students-become-tram-operators-as-germany-faces-manpower-shortage%2Farticleshow%2F108743993.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Funiversity-students-become-tram-operators-as-germany-faces-manpower-shortage%2Famp_articleshow%2F108743993.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Funiversity-students-become-tram-operators-as-germany-faces-manpower-shortage%2Famp_articleshow%2F108743993.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20Was%20In%20Tears%26quot%3B%3A%20Atishi%20Shares%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%201st%20Order%20From%20Lock-Up%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20debate%20on%20whether%20he%20can%20continue%20to%20work%20as%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20from%20prison%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20today%20issued%20his%20first%20order%20from%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate's%20(ED)%20lock-up.%C2%A0The%20order%20was%20related%20to%20the%20national%20capital's%20water%20supply%2C%20and%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20issued%20it%20through%20a%20note%20to%20Delhi%20minister%20Atishi%2C%20who%20handles%20the%20portfolio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20press%20meet%20later%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Ms%20Atishi%20said%20she%20was%20in%20tears%20on%20reading%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20note.%C2%A0%26quot%3BArvind%20Kejriwal%20ji%20has%20sent%20me%20a%20letter%20and%20a%20direction.%20On%20reading%20it%2C%20I%20was%20in%20tears.%20I%20kept%20thinking%20who%20is%20this%20man%2C%20who%20is%20in%20prison%2C%20but%20is%20still%20thinking%20about%20Delhi%20residents'%20water%20and%20sewage%20problems.%20Only%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20can%20do%20this%20because%20he%20considers%20himself%20a%20family%20member%20of%20Delhi's%202%20crore%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20BJP%2C%20you%20can%20arrest%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20put%20him%20in%20jail%2C%20but%20you%20cannot%20imprison%20his%20love%20and%20sense%20of%20duty%20for%20Delhi's%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20AAP%20leader%20may%20be%20in%20jail%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bno%20work%20will%20stop%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReading%20out%20the%20letter%2C%20she%20said%2C%C2%A0%26quot%3BArvind%20Kejriwal%20ji%20has%20written%2C%20'I%20have%20come%20to%20know%20that%20some%20areas%20of%20Delhi%20are%20facing%20water%20supply%20and%20sewer%20problems.%20I%20am%20worried%20about%20this.%20People%20should%20not%20face%20any%20problem%20because%20I%20am%20in%20jail.%20Summer%20is%20here%2C%20so%20please%20ensure%20adequate%20tankers%20in%20areas%20facing%20water%20shortage.%20Please%20give%20directions%20to%20the%20Chief%20Secretary%20and%20other%20officials%20so%20that%20people%20face%20no%20difficulty.%20People%20should%20get%20immediate%20and%20proper%20solution%20to%20their%20problems.%20Please%20seek%20help%20from%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20if%20needed.%20He%20will%20surely%20help%20you'.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20today%2C%20after%20being%20arrested%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20ji%20is%20thinking%20about%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Atishi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20by%20ED%20on%20Thursday%20night%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20Delhi's%20now-scrapped%20liquor%20policy%2C%20has%20been%20remanded%20in%20the%20central%20agency's%20custody%20for%20a%20week.%20The%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20leader%20has%20denied%20the%20allegations%20against%20him%20and%20accused%20the%20BJP-led%20central%20government%20of%20using%20probe%20agencies%20for%20political%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20Chief%20Minister%20despite%20his%20arrest.%20While%20no%20law%20bars%20him%2C%20prison%20rules%20will%20make%20it%20very%20difficult.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20law%20officer%20of%20Delhi's%20Tihar%20Jail%20says%20an%20inmate%20can%20hold%20only%20two%20meetings%20in%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRunning%20a%20government%20from%20jail%20is%20not%20straightforward.%20The%20jail%20manual%20states%20that%20you%20can%20meet%20your%20family%2C%20friends%2C%20or%20associates%20only%20twice%20a%20week.%20So%20it%20will%20not%20be%20easy%20for%20him%20to%20govern%20with%20these%20restrictions%2C%26quot%3B%20Sunil%20Gupta%20has%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%2C%20however%2C%20one%20way%20out.%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20can%20carry%20on%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20if%20he%20can%20get%20authorities%20to%20put%20him%20under%20house%20arrest.%20This%20would%2C%20however%2C%20require%20an%20approval%20from%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Vinai%20Kumar%20Saxena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Administrator%20has%20the%20authority%20to%20declare%20any%20building%20as%20a%20jail%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gupta%20said%2C%20drawing%20parallels%20with%20past%20instances%20where%20court%20complexes%20were%20designated%20as%20temporary%20jails.%20Such%20measures%20could%20help%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20continue%20to%20run%20the%20government%20from%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20such%20an%20order%20from%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor's%20office%20seems%20unlikely%2C%20given%20the%20history%20of%20face-offs%20between%20the%20Centre's%20nominee%20and%20the%20AAP%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%2C%20it%20is%20learnt%2C%20is%20examining%20ramifications%20of%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20not%20resigning.%20Legal%20experts%20said%20the%20Centre%20may%20have%20to%20suspend%20or%20remove%20him%20from%20the%20post%20since%20he%20is%20a%20public%20servant.%20This%20is%20also%20the%20procedure%20that%20is%20followed%20for%20government%20officials%20who%20are%20arrested.%20They%20are%20immediately%20suspended%20from%20service%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20is%20the%20fourth%20high-profile%20arrest%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case%2C%20after%20top%20AAP%20leaders%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20Sanjay%20Singh%20and%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20leader%20K%20Kavitha.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711257120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F1o4sf5l8_arvind-kejriwal-ani_625x300_24_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-issues-his-1st-order-from-enforcement-directorate-lock-up-5300295%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20debate%20on%20whether%20he%20can%20continue%20to%20work%20as%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20from%20prison%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20today%20issued%20his%20first%20order%20from%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate's%20(ED)%