he%20BJP%20between%20April%20and%20May%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Eearlier%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Ftop-electoral-bond-purchasers-include-some-companies-that-were-raided-or-under-the-scanner%5C%22%3E%20reported%20%3C%2Fa%3Ethat%20the%20income%20tax%20department%20conducted%20%E2%80%9Cinspection%E2%80%9D%20at%20its%20offices%20in%20October%202019.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20company%20donated%20Rs%20980%20crore%20as%20electoral%20bonds%20and%20also%20received%20key%20government%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20top%20donors%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20this%20period%20include%20Vedanta%20Limited%20that%20donated%20Rs%2052.65%20crore%20to%20the%20party%2C%20Essel%20Mining%20and%20Industries%20Limited%20that%20donated%20Rs%2050%20crores%2C%20and%20Bajaj%20Group%20and%20PHL%20Fininvest%20Private%20Limited%20that%20donated%20Rs%2040%20crore%20each.%20Industrialist%20Laxmi%20Niwas%20Mittal%20gave%20Rs%2035%20crore%20while%20Sun%20Pharma%20Laboratories%20Limited%20gave%20Rs%2031.5%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20real%20estate%20conglomerate%20Robert%20Vadra%E2%80%99s%20DLF%20group%20(DLF%20Commercial%20Developers%20Limited%20and%20DLF%20Luxury%20Homes%20Limited)%20paid%20Rs%2025%20crore%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20this%20period.%20They%20only%20paid%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1065652%2Fafter-rs-170-crore-to-bjp-real-estate-firm-dlf-got-clean-chit-in-vadra-deal-from-haryana%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520September%25202018%252C%2520the%2520Haryana%2Cin%2520land%2520deals%2520in%2520Gurugram.%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EScroll.in%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereports%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20in%20January%202019%2C%20DLF%20offices%20were%20searched%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20for%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20a%20land%20allocation%20case.%20The%20payment%20of%20Rs%2025%20crore%20took%20place%20between%20April%20and%20May%202019.%20The%20group%20had%20been%20under%20a%20cloud%20after%20a%20Haryana%20officer%20called%20off%20a%20land%20deal%20it%20had%20struck%20with%20former%20Congress%20president%20Sonia%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20son-in-law%20Robert%20Vadra%E2%80%99s%20Sky%20Light%20for%203.5%20acres%20on%20September%2018%2C%202012%2C%20triggering%20a%20public%20outcry.%20The%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20state%20government%20in%20Haryana%20also%20initiated%20action.%20In%20April%20last%20year%2C%20the%20high%20court%20was%20told%20that%20no%20law%20was%20violated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20Piramal%20Group%2C%20in%20which%20Reliance%E2%80%99s%20Mukesh%20Ambani%E2%80%99s%20son-in-law%20Anand%20Piramal%20is%20a%20director%2C%20gave%20Rs%2020%20crore%20to%20the%20BJP%20through%20Piramal%20Capital%20and%20Housing%20Finance%20Limited%20and%20Piramal%20Enterprises%20Limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fonly-three-parties-had-opened-an-sbi-bank-account-for-electoral-bonds-till-march-31-2018-rti%5C%22%3EOnly%20Three%20Parties%20Had%20Opened%20an%20SBI%20Bank%20Account%20For%20Electoral%20Bonds%20Till%20March%2031%2C%202018%3A%20RTI%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20got%20the%20most%20bonds%20from%20Jalan%2C%20firms%20linked%20to%20Adani%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20received%20a%20paltry%203.2%25%20of%20the%20total%20bonds%20received%2C%20i.e.%2C%20Rs%2095.29%20crore.%20Of%20this%2C%20the%20highest%20amount%20of%20Rs%2020%20crore%20came%20from%20Jalan%E2%80%99s%20Keventer%20Food%20Park%20Infra%20Limited%20and%20Rs%2010%20crore%20came%20from%20Madanlal%20Limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Congress%20president%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20accused%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20of%20favouring%20the%20business%20interests%20of%20billionaire%20Gautam%20Adani.%20Data%20shows%20that%20the%20party%20encashed%20Rs%208%20crore%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adanienterprises.com%2Fnewsroom%2Fmedia-releases%2Fadani-welspun-discovers-gas-in-mumbai%5C%22%3Efirms%20linked%20to%20Adani%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20received%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%208%20crore%20before%20the%202019%20elections%20from%20Welspun%20Corp%20Limited%20and%20Welspun%20Enterprises%20Limited.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.adanienterprises.com%2Fnewsroom%2Fmedia-releases%2Fadani-welspun-discovers-gas-in-mumbai%5C%22%3Epress%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Adani%20Enterprises%E2%80%99%20website%2C%20dated%20April%202021%2C%20talks%20about%20gas%20exploration%20in%20the%20Mumbai%20offshore%20block%20by%20Adani%20Welspun%20Exploration%20Limited%20%E2%80%93%20a%20joint%20venture%20between%20the%20Adani%20group%20and%20Welspun%20Enterprises%20Ltd%20with%2065%3A35%20holdings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20also%20received%20Rs%205%20crore%20from%20Piramal%20Group%E2%80%99s%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zaubacorp.com%2Fcompany%2FPRL-Developers-Private-Limited%2FU45400MH2011PTC216545%23google_vignette%5C%22%3E%20PRL%20Developers%20Private%20Limited%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Other%20top%20donors%20to%20the%20Congress%20include%20Bharati%20Airtel%20that%20donated%20Rs%208%20crore%2C%20MEIL%20that%20gave%20Rs%205%20crore%2C%20and%20Mumbai-based%20Modern%20Road%20Makers%20Private%20Limited%20that%20gave%20Rs%206%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECement%20manufacturing%20giant%20from%20the%20North-East%2C%20Star%20Cement%20Meghalaya%20Limited%20also%20gave%20Rs%204.5%20crore%20to%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%20of%20receiving%20these%20bonds%2C%20the%20party%20held%20governments%20in%20Punjab%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Karnataka%2C%20Manipur%2C%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fparties-got-rs-rs-7726-cr-in-non-electoral-bond-funds-between-2013-23-nearly-65-went-to-the-bjp%5C%22%3E%20Parties%20Got%20Rs%207%2C726%20Cr%20in%20Non-electoral%20Bond%20Funds%20Between%202013-23%2C%20Nearly%2065%25%20Went%20to%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJalan%E2%80%99s%20Keventer%20and%20ITC%20among%20top%20TMC%20donors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TMC%2C%20which%20has%20received%20the%20second%20highest%20electoral%20bonds%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20and%20saw%20its%20f%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftop-five-political-parties-saw-electoral-bonds-fortunes-turning-with-election-wins-and-losses%5C%22%3Eortunes%20rising%20after%20the%202021%20assembly%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20benefited%20from%20Jalan%E2%80%99s%20firms%20before%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJalan%E2%80%99s%20Keventer%20Food%20Park%20Infra%20Limited%20was%20the%20top%20donor%20to%20the%20party%20before%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20gave%20a%20total%20of%20Rs%2020%20crore%20of%20the%20total%20Rs%2036.20%20crore%20that%20the%20party%20received%20during%20this%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20top%20donors%20to%20the%20TMC%20include%20the%20largest%20carbon%20manufacturer%20in%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20Philips%20Carbon%20Black%20Limited.%20It%20gave%20Rs%205%20crore%20to%20the%20party.%20Kolkata%20based-ITC%20Limited%20gave%20Rs%204.95%20crore%20to%20the%20party%20during%20this%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJalan%E2%80%99s%20firms%20also%20donated%20to%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20only%20encashed%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%2010%20crore%2C%20all%20of%20them%20came%20from%20Jalan%E2%80%99s%20Keventer%20Food%20Park%20Infra%20Limited.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%2C%20which%20encashed%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%208.45%20crore%2C%20received%20the%20most%20from%20Piramal%20Group%E2%80%99s%20PRL%20Developers%20Private%20Limited%20at%20Rs%205%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiromani%20Akal