important%20common%20understandings%20on%20growing%20the%20China-Nepal%20relations%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lin%20continued%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20of%20Shrestha%E2%80%99s%20visit%20also%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20China%20is%20suggesting%20Nepal%20to%20sign%20an%20implementation%20plan%20of%20the%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Nepal%20is%20unlikely%20to%20sign%20the%20agreement%20ahead%20of%20a%20planned%20investment%20summit%20for%20which%20it%20is%20seeking%20the%20support%20of%20the%20international%20community%2C%20including%20India%2C%20the%20US%20and%20other%20democratic%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20was%20the%20first%20country%20to%20react%20on%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20new%20coalition%20in%20Nepal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20series%20of%20statements%20from%20Beijing%2C%20along%20with%20meetings%20between%20Chinese%20officials%20and%20Nepali%20ministers%20during%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20new%20coalition%2C%20suggest%20that%20Beijing%20is%20optimistic%20following%20the%20emergence%20of%20a%20Left-dominated%20government%20in%20Kathmandu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Dahal%20abandoned%20the%20Nepali%20Congress%2C%20opting%20instead%20to%20forge%20a%20new%20coalition%20with%20the%20CPN-UML%20and%20other%20parties%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20dominant%20presence%20of%20two%20key%20communist%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20the%20CPN%20(Maoist%20Center)%20and%20the%20CPN-UML%20%E2%80%93%20alongside%20the%20CPN%20(Unified%20Socialist)%2C%20albeit%20with%20support%20from%20non-communist%20parties%20like%20the%20Janata%20Samajbadi%20Party%20and%20the%20Rastriya%20Swantra%20Party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20been%20favouring%20a%20communist-led%20government%20in%20Kathmandu%20in%20recent%20years.%20This%20week%2C%20the%20new%20coalition%20unveiled%20a%20common%20minimum%20program%20(CMP)%2C%20outlining%20its%20commitment%20to%20an%20independent%20and%20non-aligned%20foreign%20policy%20grounde