th%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Farvind-kejriwal-arrest-second-sitting-cm-lok-sabha-polls%5C%22%3Earrest%20of%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Delhi%20and%20the%20main%20leader%20of%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20once%20again%20made%20it%20very%20clear%20that%20it%20would%20not%20allow%20any%20major%20political%20leader%20or%20party%20to%20remain%20in%20a%20position%20to%20campaign%20for%20the%20forthcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Kejriwal%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Jharkhand%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjharkhand-cm-hemant-soren-arrest-likely-ed%5C%22%3EHemant%20Soren%2C%20was%20arrested%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20another%20%E2%80%98corruption%E2%80%99%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKejriwal%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20was%20imminent.%20The%20ED%20had%20been%20issuing%20summons%20to%20him%20and%20the%20courts%20refused%20to%20restrain%20the%20agency.%20Even%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20had%20burnt%20the%20midnight%20oil%20to%20save%20Arnab%20Goswami%E2%80%99s%20liberty%2C%20asked%20Kejriwal%E2%80%99s%20lawyers%20not%20to%20disturb%20its%20sleep%20and%20come%20the%20next%20morning.%20Meanwhile%2C%20he%20was%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20supposed%20to%20believe%20that%20all%20this%20is%20part%20of%20due%20process%20in%20investigating%20the%20alleged%20crime%20of%20changing%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20liquor%20policy%20for%20monetary%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20leaders%20of%20the%20AAP%20have%20already%20been%20arrested%20and%20are%20in%20jail.%20Another%20leader%20of%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20from%20Telangana%20is%20also%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20arrests%20of%20people%20like%20Anand%20Teltumbde%2C%20father%20Stan%20Swamy%2C%20Hany%20Babu%2C%20Sharjeel%20Imam%20and%20Umar%20Khalid%2C%20jurists%20have%20been%20asking%20again%20and%20again%20as%20to%20why%20the%20government%20needs%20to%20arrest%20people%20and%20keep%20them%20in%20jail%20only%20because%20it%20needs%20them%20for%20investigation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20always%20ask%20them%20to%20join%20the%20investigation.%20Persons%20like%20them%2C%20or%20Kejriwal%20or%20Soren%2C%20are%20not%20fleeing%20out%20of%20the%20country.%20Why%20do%20agencies%20want%20them%20to%20be%20in%20jail%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FFlEhy_QHQzs%3Fsi%3DbDxgPnCNNPvva2wr%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20India%20and%20especially%20under%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20investigation%20is%20used%20as%20a%20ruse%20to%20punish%20the%20critics%20and%20opponents%20of%20the%20government%20by%20jailing%20them.%20This%20is%20exactly%20what%20was%20done%20to%20P.%20Chidambaram%20and%20many%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20we%20heard%20the%20agencies%20informing%20the%20court%20that%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Felgar-parishad-case-after-opposing-bail-for-years-nia-now-says-it-doesnt-need-custody-of-shoma-sen%5C%22%3Edid%20not%20need%20Shoma%20Sen%E2%80%99s%20custody%20for%20investigation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20is%20in%20jail%20for%20more%20than%20five%20years%20in%20the%20Bhima%20Koregaon%20conspiracy%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20mind%20boggling%20that%20the%20agency%20can%2C%20after%20putting%20a%20person%20in%20jail%20for%20five%20years%2C%20tell%20the%20court%20with%20a%20straight%20face%20that%20her%20custody%20is%20not%20required!%20And%20there%20is%20no%20uproar%20in%20society!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20it%20is%20this%20understanding%20of%20the%20popular%20mind%20that%20encourages%20the%20BJP%20to%20go%20on%20perpetrating%20more%20and%20more%20atrocities%20against%20its%20critics%20and%20opposition%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20masses%20do%20not%20care%20for%20their%20liberty.%20They%20still%20think%20that%20the%20government%20owns%20them%20and%20can%20do%20anything%20it%20wants%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20before%20Kejriwal%E2%80%99s%20arrest%2C%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20issued%20statements%20that%20all%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20bank%20accounts%20had%20been%20frozen%20and%20the%20party%20was%20left%20with%20no%20money%20to%20do%20even%20its%20basic%20organisational%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20also%20reported%20that%20income%20tax%20officials%20went%20from%20bank%20to%20bank%20and%20arm%20twisted%20them%20to%20transfer%20money%20from%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20accounts%20to%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20an%20extraordinary%20step.%20We%20have%20not%20heard%20that%20banks%2C%20without%20even%20informing%20their%20clients%2C%20would%20allow%20their%20money%20to%20be%20transferred%20to%20another%20account.%20It%20is%20as%20if%20the%20government%20is%20telling%20us%20that%20it%20owns%20everything%20we%20have.%20The%20government%20here%20is%20behaving%20like%20an%20extortionist.%20It%20can%20seize%20your%20account%2C%20it%20can%20take%20away%20money%20from%20it%20and%20it%20can%20arrest%20you%20when%20it%20wants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20turning%20into%20mere%20properties%20of%20the%20government%20and%20do%20not%20realise%20what%20it%20is%20that%20we%20are%20losing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FsLRO4qs6Q-Q%3Fsi%3D91h1qyULQm41LVus%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDemocracy%20runs%20on%20the%20principles%20of%20bipartisanship%20and%20the%20autonomy%20of%20institutions.%20It%20means%20the%20existence%20of%20an%20opposition%20and%20the%20acceptance%20by%20the%20government%20of%20the%20legitimacy%20of%20its%20voice%20and%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20we%20see%20is%20a%20BJP%20government%20which%20wants%20a%20political%20field%20empty%20of%20the%20opposition%20and%20to%20be%20the%20only%20player.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20saw%20it%20being%20done%20in%20the%20parliament%E2%80%99s%20winter%20session%2C%20in%20which%20nearly%20all%20of%20the%20opposition%20was%20forced%20out.%20We%20saw%20the%20farcical%20proceedings%20of%20the%20cancellation%20of%20Mahua%20Moitra%E2%80%99s%20parliamentary%20membership.%20Then%20we%20saw%20the%20blatant%20change%20in%20the%20policy%20of%20the%20selection%20of%20election%20commissioners.%20This%20is%20just%20before%20elections.%20And%20we%20saw%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20refusal%20to%20intervene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20we%20think%20that%20this%20is%20a%20football%20match%20or%20some%20kind%20of%20wrestling%20between%20the%20opposition%20and%20the%20government%2C%20we%20are%20mistaken.%20The%20opposition%20also%20represents%20the%20people.%20An%20election%20victory%20does%20not%20allow%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20disable%20the%20opposition%20by%20using%20the%20coercive%20instruments%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20knows%20that%20the%20arrest%20of%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20or%20Hemant%20Soren%20is%20to%20scare%20political%20leaders%20and%20the%20people%20and%20stun%20them%20into%20inaction.%20It%20is%20also%20to%20stifle%20their%20voice%20when%20it%20is%20needed%20the%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFreezing%20the%20bank%20accounts%20of%20a%20party%20means%20freezing%20all%20of%20its%20movements.%20It%20cannot%20print%20a%20leaflet%2C%20its%20leaders%20cannot%20travel%20and%20its%20offices%20cannot%20function.%20But%20is%20it%20harming%20them%3F%20They%20function%20for%20us!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20would%20be%20good%20to%20hear%20what%20Salman%20Soz%2C%20a%20Congress%20leader%2C%20said%20after%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20bank%20accounts%20were%20frozen%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20think%20it%20is%20just%20the%20problem%20of%20the%20Congress%20Party%20that%20its%20accounts%20have%20been%20emptied%20out%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%20then%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20understand%20how%20economies%20function.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20will%20have%20a%20snowball%20effect%20with%20businesses%20and%20individuals%20feeling%20insecure%20(remember%20the%20retrospective%20tax%3F).%20If%20the%20government%20can%20do%20it%20with%20the%20main%20opposition%20party%2C%20one%20which%20has%20the%20support%20of%20millions%20of%20people%2C%20imagine%20what%20the%20government%20can%20do%20to%20an%20individual%20company%20or%20taxpayer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20you%20may%20say%20that%20I%20have%20done%20nothing%20wrong%20and%20why%20will%20the%20government%20come%20after%20my%20business%20or%20my%20family%E2%80%99s%20finances.%20But%20that%20is%20not%20how%20this%20works.%20Once%20this%20tiger%20tastes%20blood%2C%20its%20lust%20only%20grows.%20It%20looks%20for%20blood%20everywhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20already%20seen%20how%20electoral%20bonds%20were%20purchased%20by%20companies%20that%20were%20also%20raided%20by%20agencies.%20This%20will%20not%20remain%20confined%20to%20such%20companies%20but%20will%20keep%20spreading%20and%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20anyone%20will%20remain%20immune%20from%20a%20feeling%20of%20insecurity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20we%20will%20live%20at%20the%20mercy%20of%20those%20wielding%20power.%20Even%20when%20we%20have%20done%20nothing%20wrong%2C%20and%20most%20people%20just%20want%20to%20live%20their%20lives%20peacefully%2C%20we%20will%20have%20to%20live%20according%20to%20the%20dictates%20of%20the%20Hafta%20Vasooli%20gang.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIs%20this%20how%20we%20want%20to%20live%3F%20Are%20we%20actors%20in%20this%20theatre%20of%20democracy%20or%20mere%20spectators%3F%20Have%20we%20turned%20into%20such%20imbeciles%20who%20get%20overawed%20by%20these%20strong-arm%20and%20clearly%20criminal%20acts%20of%20the%20party%20in%20power%20and%20clap%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWill%20Kejriwal%E2%80%99s%20arrest%20force%20the%20people%20to%20come%20out%20of%20their%20slumber%3F%20Will%20the%20streets%20wake%20up%3F%20For%20this%20is%20the%20moment%20for%20the%20people%20to%20rise%20and%20save%20the%20opposition.%20For%20its%20own%20sake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fapoorvanand%5C%22%3EApoorvanand%3C%2Fa%3E%20teaches%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711123520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F15115004%2FScreenshot-2023-11-15-at-11.49.15-AM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkejriwal-arrest-this-coup-against-our-constitutional-setup-is-a-wake-up-call%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20knows%20that%20the%20arrest%20of%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20or%20Hemant%20Soren%20is%20to%20scare%20political%20leaders%20and%20the%20people%20and%20stun%20them%20into%20inaction.%20Is%20this%20how%20we%20want%20to%20live%3F%20Are%20we%20actors%20in%20this%20theatre%20of%20democracy%20or%20mere%20spectators%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fkejriwal-arrest-this-coup-against-our-constitutional-setup-is-a-wake-up-call%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Gaza%20ceasefire%20vote%20-%20why%20did%20it%20fail%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711122600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F1600x900%2F2372403220643623907_6497979.png%3F20240322181804%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fus-gaza-ceasefire-vote-why-did-it-fail-13099959%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%C2%A0US%20has