20with%20chief%20minister%20and%20Telangana%20Congress%20committee%20president%20A.%20Revanth%20Reddy%20while%20accepting%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20colours%2C%20he%20was%20declared%20its%20candidate%20from%20Secunderabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRS%20has%20now%20petitioned%20assembly%20speaker%20G.%20Prasad%20Kumar%20seeking%20Nagender%E2%80%99s%20disqualification%20as%20per%20the%20anti-defection%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20other%20BRS%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20G.%20Ranjith%20Reddy%2C%20the%20sitting%20MP%20from%20Chevella%20and%20a%20major%20player%20in%20the%20poultry%20industry%3B%20and%20G.%20Sunitha%20Mahender%20Reddy%2C%20who%20is%20the%20zilla%20parishad%20chairperson%20of%20Vikarabad%20district%20%E2%80%93%20also%20got%20tickets%20as%20Congress%20candidates%20from%20Chevella%20and%20Malkajgiri%20constituencies%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERanjith%20Reddy%20and%20Nagender%20joined%20the%20Congress%20on%20the%20same%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunitha%20Mahender%20Reddy%2C%20wife%20of%20BRS%20MLC%20and%20former%20minister%20Mahender%20Reddy%2C%20was%20earlier%20sounded%20out%20for%20a%20Congress%20ticket%20from%20Chevella%20but%20was%20accommodated%20at%20Malkajgiri%2C%20reportedly%20against%20her%20wishes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Nagender%2C%20Mahender%20Reddy%20has%20also%20not%20resigned%20from%20the%20legislative%20council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Congress%20MP%20from%20Nagarkurnool%20(SC%20reserved)%20Mallu%20Ravi%20was%20renominated%20from%20the%20same%20constituency%20while%20Gaddam%20Vamshi%20Krishna%20was%20selected%20from%20Peddapalli%20(SC)%2C%20a%20constituency%20represented%20thrice%20by%20his%20grandfather%20and%20former%20Union%20minister%20Venkatswamy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20will%20begin%20his%20political%20career%20straight%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20former%20Congress%20MLA%2C%20A.%20Sampath%20Kumar%20was%20overlooked%20for%20the%20Nagarkurnool%20seat%2C%20though%20he%20wrote%20a%20letter%20to%20former%20party%20president%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20requesting%20his%20candidature%20to%20be%20considered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20all%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20is%20making%20a%20strong%20bid%20to%20repeat%20its%20performance%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%2C%20has%20set%20its%20eyes%20on%20winning%20horses%20in%20its%20selection%20of%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20poured%20cold%20water%20on%20the%20ambition%20of%20former%20Hyderabad%20mayor%20Bonthu%20Rammohan%20and%20his%20wife%20Sridevi%2C%20a%20corporator%2C%20in%20getting%20a%20ticket%20from%20Secunderabad%20after%20the%20couple%20had%20quit%20the%20BRS%20last%20month%20to%20join%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20so%20far%20selected%20candidates%20for%20nine%20out%20of%2017%20parliamentary%20constituencies%20in%20Telangana%20that%20will%20go%20to%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20played%20it%20safe%20in%20its%20earlier%20list%20of%20four%20candidates%20by%20selecting%20Vamshi%20Chand%20Reddy%20for%20Mahabubnagar%2C%20former%20Union%20minister%20of%20state%20P.%20Balram%20Naik%20for%20Mahabubabad%2C%20former%20Congress%20legislature%20party%20leader%20K.%20Jana%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20son%20Raghuveer%20for%20Nalgonda%20and%20former%20MP%20Suresh%20Shetkar%20for%20Zaheerabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20them%20got%20tickets%20on%20their%20home%20turfs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20selection%20became%20tough%20with%20leaders%20from%20the%20BRS%20joining%20the%20Congress%20in%20a%20big%20way%20as%20the%20party%20consolidated%20its%20position%20after%20winning%20the%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20minister%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20declaration%20that%20he%20has%20%E2%80%9Copened%20the%20flood%20gates%E2%80%9D%20for%20entrants%20into%20the%20party%20received%20instant%20reactions%20from%20leaders%20like%20Nagender%20and%20Ranjith%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20trend%20is%20any%20indication%2C%20sources%20said%20more%20surprises%20were%20in%20store%20in%20the%20selection%20of%20candidates%20for%20the%20remaining%20eight%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20stake%2C%20notably%2C%20was%20the%20selection%20for%20Nizamabad%20seat%2C%20where%20former%20minister%20T.%20Jeevan%20Reddy%20is%20a%20strong%20aspirant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20play%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20also%20poaching%20candidates%20from%20the%20BRS%20to%20make%20its%20lineup%20strong.%20Both%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20are%20preying%20on%20the%20BRS%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20outsmart%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20gave%20tickets%20to%20two%20sitting%20MPs%2C%20two%20former%20MPs%20and%20a%20former%20MLA%20of%20the%20BRS%20who%20joined%20the%20party%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20strong%20contender%2C%20winning%20eight%20seats%20and%20obtaining%20a%20vote%20share%20of%2014%25%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls.%20The%20Congress%20won%2064%20seats%20and%20polled%2039.7%25%20of%20the%20vote%2C%20while%20the%20BRS%20won%2039%20seats%20and%20polled%2037.6%25%20of%20the%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20assembly%20has%20119%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20stakes%20for%20the%20BJP%20have%20gone%20up%20in%20the%20coming%20elections%20with%20the%20arrest%20of%20BRS%20MLC%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%E2%80%99s%20daughter%2C%20K.%20Kavitha%2C%20in%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leaders%20were%20often%20confronted%20with%20questions%20on%20differential%20treatment%20for%20Kavitha%20by%20not%20arresting%20her%2C%20while%20the%20other%20accused%20in%20the%20case%2C%20including%20former%20Delhi%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20languished%20in%20jail%20for%20over%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20expressed%20relief%20that%20the%20question%20did%20not%20haunt%20them%20anymore%20and%20that%20they%20could%20freely%20approach%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20a