on%20Friday%20(March%2022)%20announced%20former%20IPS%20officer%20R.S.%20Praveen%20Kumar%20as%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20candidate%20from%20Nagarkurnool.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Praveen%20Kumar%20resigned%20as%20the%20state%20president%20of%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20to%20join%20the%20BRS%20recently.%20He%20had%20even%20negotiated%20an%20alliance%20between%20the%20BRS%20and%20BSP%20along%20with%20BSP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%20Ramji%20Gautam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20day%20later%2C%20Kumar%20announced%20his%20resignation%20from%20the%20BSP%2C%20saying%20party%20supremo%20Mayawati%20had%20mounted%20pressure%20on%20him%20to%20call%20off%20the%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alliance%20contemplated%20the%20allotment%20of%20Nagarkurnool%20and%20Hyderabad%20seats%20to%20the%20BSP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERao%20also%20announced%20the%20candidature%20of%20former%20IAS%20officer%20and%20now%20MLC%20P.%20Venkatarami%20Reddy%20from%20the%20Medak%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1711119638000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F22200254%2FSMR-II.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-congress-no-exception-in-wolfing-brs-defectors-for-a-strong-lineup%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Three%20out%20of%20five%20candidates%20announced%20by%20the%20Congress%20high%20command%20in%20its%20third%20list%20on%20Thursday%20are%20defectors%20from%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samiti.%20The%20BJP%20is%20also%20poaching%20candidates%20from%20the%20BRS%20to%20make%20its%20lineup%20strong.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-congress-no-exception-in-wolfing-brs-defectors-for-a-strong-lineup%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aditya%20Birla%20Group%2C%20Rashmi%2C%20and%20Jindal%20Steel%20Power%20Top%20Poll%20Bond%20Donors%20of%20Bij