e%20than%20one-third%20is%20prone%20to%20forest%20fires.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPreventing%20fires%20through%20community%20participation%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20THF%E2%80%99s%20intervention%2C%20Pritam%2C%20like%20many%20other%20volunteers%2C%20was%20provided%20comprehensive%20training%20to%20tackle%20forest%20fires.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20he%20was%20better%20equipped%20and%20prepared%20for%20any%20untoward%20incidents%20similar%20to%20those%20that%20occurred%20in%202022%20and%20was%20able%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20emergency%20and%20control%20potential%20fire%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20educated%20on%20how%20to%20implement%20local%20mitigation%20strategies%20to%20effectively%20control%20any%20forest%20fire.%20We%20were%20provided%20with%20firefighting%20kits%20that%20included%20a%20set%20of%20different%20types%20of%20fire%20rakes%2C%20a%20modified%20sickle%2C%20a%20shovel%2C%20a%20fire%20beater%2C%20and%20a%20tool%20kit%20bag.%20Training%20was%20provided%20on%20fire%20line%20development%2C%20biomass%20management%2C%20safety%20measures%20during%20fire%20dousing%2C%20and%20uses%20of%20the%20various%20equipment%20that%20were%20provided%20to%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20he%20responds%20to%20the%20emergency%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20inform%20the%20forest%20department%20about%20any%20forest%20fires%20that%20occur%20in%20the%20area.%20Meanwhile%2C%20we%20start%20clearing%20broad%20strips%20of%20land%20of%20all%20inflammable%20material%20like%20dry%20leaves%20and%20fodder%20so%20that%20fire%20does%20not%20extend%20from%20one%20area%20to%20another.%20After%20making%20forest%20lines%2C%20we%20also%20throw%20sand%20to%20extinguish%20the%20fire.%20However%2C%20if%20the%20fire%20is%20on%20a%20large%20scale%2C%20we%20try%20to%20prevent%20it%20from%20spreading%20further%20rather%20than%20extinguishing%20it.%E2%80