0felt%20that%20the%20community%20needed%20our%20help%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20brothers%20were%20very%20sure%20of%20their%20idea%2C%20their%20friends%20and%20family%20were%20a%20little%20sceptical.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20something%20which%20was%20not%20the%20plan%20of%20our%20family%20for%20us.%20It%20became%20very%20difficult%20for%20them%20to%20understand%20the%20need%20for%20such%20a%20shift.%20Additionally%2C%20back%20when%20we%20started%20in%202016%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20organic%20farming%2C%20the%20conservation%20of%20native%20trees%20was%20not%20very%20popular%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20had%20an%20urge%20to%20go%20for%20it%20anyway.%20In%202016%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20start%20%E2%80%98Monk%20Bouffe%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20bringing%20tribal%20produce%20to%20the%20right%20buyers%2C%20and%20have%20never%20looked%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENatural%2C%20organic%20and%20edible%20Holi%20colours%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20one%20of%20their%20conservation%20efforts%20across%20the%20tribal%20areas%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chattisgarh%2C%20the%20duo%20encountered%20people%20from%20the%20Bhil%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20community%2C%20based%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Udaipur%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20consists%20of%20a%20small%20number%20of%20members.%20Among%20other%20skills%2C%20they%20possess%20an%20incredible%20talent%20for%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F344915%2Fhow-to-prepare-natural-holi-colours-at-home-from-beetroot-spinach-turmeric%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20handcrafting%20natural%20colours%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20Gaurang%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20skill%20was%20dwindling%20due%20to%20the%20prevalence%20of%20synthetic%20colours%20in%20the