the%20Forest%20Rights%20Act%20was%20enacted%20and%20it%20stated%20that%20any%20member%20or%20community%20that%20primarily%20resided%20in%20forest%20land%20for%20bona%20fide%20livelihood%20needs%20before%2013%20December%2C%202005%2C%20would%20be%20entitled%20to%20forest%20rights.%20%E2%80%9CUsing%20the%20ISRO%20images%2C%20we%20understood%20that%20these%20people%20settled%20here%20after%20that%20period%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-2-1710829041.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jain%20shares%20200%20encroachers%20were%20evicted%20and%20at%20least%20600%20hectares%20of%20forest%20land%20was%20recovered%20in%20the%20past%20one%20year.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-2-1710829041.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-2-1710829041-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-2-1710829041-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-2-1710829041-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-2-1710829041-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345149%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EJain%20shares%20200%20encroachers%20were%20evicted%20in%20the%20past%20one%20year.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20this%20period%2C%20Jain%20informs%20that%20the%20forest%20cover%20reduced%20from%20400%20trees%20per%20hectare%20to%2040%20trees%20per%20hectare.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20necessary%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20encroachments%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%