%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-5-1710829219.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22With%20the%20help%20of%20forest%20guards%2C%20Jain%20was%20able%20to%20recover%20600%20hectares%20of%20forest%20land.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-5-1710829219.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-5-1710829219-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-5-1710829219-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-5-1710829219-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2FVarun-Jain-5-1710829219-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-345152%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20forest%20guards%2C%20Jain%20was%20able%20to%20recover%20600%20hectares%20of%20forest%20land.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20order%20dated%2012%20December%2C%202023%2C%20by%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20Forest%20and%20Climate%20Change%20Department%20mentioned%20that%20with%20ISRO%20images%2C%20it%20was%20evident%20that%20the%20forest%20land%20was%20encroached%20after%202005%20and%20the%20documentation%20of%20petitioners%20does%20not%20support%20their%20claims%20on%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJain%20informs%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F176709%2Fifs-civil-servant-hero-sikkim-nrega-sandeep-tambe%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eforest%20official%20%3C%2Fa%3Econducted%20the%20first%20evic