eservation%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%224000%2B%20People%20Are%20Getting%20Life-Saving%20Dialysis%20Through%20This%20Amazing%20Initiative%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20The%20Hans%20Foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChandrakala%20Devi%2C%20an%20ASHA%20worker%20from%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Chamoli%20district%2C%20started%20experiencing%20severe%20body%20pain%2C%20fever%2C%20chills%2C%20nausea%2C%20and%20difficulty%20walking%20in%20late%202021.%20During%20the%20course%20of%20her%20work%20in%20her%20district%2C%20these%20symptoms%20caused%20her%20considerable%20discomfort%20and%20made%20it%20difficult%20for%20her%20to%20continue%20her%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20visited%20nearby%20doctors%20and%20PHCs%2C%20who%20ordered%20some%20basic%20tests%20and%20prescribed%20medicines.%20After%20two%20weeks%20of%20rest%20at%20home%2C%20the%2045-year-old%20did%20not%20experience%20any%20improvement.%20A%20doctor%20advised%20her%20to%20visit%20a%20hospital%20in%20Dehradun%20for%20better%20access%20to%20treatment%2C%20which%20involved%20travelling%20almost%20four%20hours%20to%20cover%20a%20distance%20of%20over%20150%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20Government-aided%20hospital%20in%20Dehradun%2C%20Chandrakala%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F140950%2Findian-scientists-develop-sensor-for-early-detection-of-chronic-kidney-disease%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echronic%20kidney%20disease%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20advised%20dialysis%20twice%20a%20week.%20As%20this%20treatment%20was%20not%20available%20near%20her%20residence%2C%20she%20had%20to%20travel%20to%20Dehradun%20and%20stay%20there%20for%20two%20nights%20every%20week%20to%20get%20the%20dialysis%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20single%20mother%2C%20being%20separated%20from%20her%20son%2C%20spending%20on%20travel%2C